T02TD1360E:156a-1: shr'i k'a la tsa kra mandala bhi dhi:/
T02TD1360E:156a-3: dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga / dpal dus kyi 'khor lo la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1360E:156a-4: gang gi gsung gi 'od zer gyis //
T02TD1360E:156a-6: spyan ras gzigs la phyag 'tshal nas //
T02TD1360E:156a-7: dkyil 'khor cho ga dbye bar bya //
T02TD1360E:156a-8: yan lag bzhi pa'i sgrub thabs kyis //
T02TD1360E:156a-9: sngon du bsnyen pa byas nas su //
T02TD1360E:156a-11: dkyil 'khor yang ni rnam pa gnyis //
T02TD1360E:156a-12: lhag gnas dang ni mchod pa'o //
T02TD1360E:156a-13: lhag gnas la yang rnam gnyis te //
T02TD1360E:156a-14: rang don dang ni gzhan don no //
T02TD1360E:156a-15: mchod pa la yang rnam gnyis te //
T02TD1360E:156a-16: bdag sgrub dang ni gzhan sgrub po //
T02TD1360E:156a-17: sngon 'gro dngos dang rjes dang ni //
T02TD1360E:156a-18: yan lag la sogs thun mong ngo //
T02TD1360E:156a-19: dang por slob dpon brtag pa ni //
T02TD1360E:156a-20: slob dpon yang ni dam tshig can //
T02TD1360E:156a-21: rdo rje'i theg pa dang por zhon //
T02TD1360E:156a-22: de nyid khyab can chags pa med //
T02TD1360E:156a-23: dri ma dang ni rnam par bral //
T02TD1360E:156a-24: bzod dang tshul khrims don 'jug pa //
T02TD1360E:156a-25: slob ma rnams la bde ster zhing //
T02TD1360E:156a-26: dmyal ba yi ni 'jigs sel ba //
T02TD1360E:156a-27: de kho na yi tshangs spyod can //
T02TD1360E:156a-28: bdud rnams kyi ni rdo rje dbyug / de yang sa yi steng du ni //
T02TD1360E:156a-29: rdo rje sems dpa' rab tu grags //
T02TD1360E:156a-30: khro dang nga rgyal dang ldan zhing //
T02TD1360E:156a-31: dam tshig dang ni rnam bral ba //
T02TD1360E:156a-32: rdzas la brkam zhing ma thos pa //
T02TD1360E:156a-33: slob ma rnams ni bslu don du //
T02TD1360E:156b-0: @156b mchog tu bde ba'i go 'phang du //
T02TD1360E:156b-1: sems ni nyams dang dbang ma bskur //
T02TD1360E:156b-2: longs spyod chags shing myos pa dang //
T02TD1360E:156b-3: zher 'debs pa yi tshig smra zhing //
T02TD1360E:156b-4: rang dbang don du 'dod spyod pa //
T02TD1360E:156b-5: slob ma rdzogs byang chub don du //
T02TD1360E:156b-6: dmyal ba lta bur rtogs pa yis //
T02TD1360E:156b-7: de ni spang bar bya ba yin //
T02TD1360E:156b-8: zab cing rgya che ba yi sems //
T02TD1360E:156b-9: bla ma mnyes pa la dga' zhing //
T02TD1360E:156b-10: gtong ba'i sems dang yon tan che //
T02TD1360E:156b-11: thar pa 'dod cing rgyud la dad //
T02TD1360E:156b-12: sems ni g-yo ba med pa dang //
T02TD1360E:156b-13: de nyid rnyed pa dang gsang zhing //
T02TD1360E:156b-14: gdug pa rnams kyi tshogs bral ba //
T02TD1360E:156b-15: shin tu mkhas pa'i bla ma yis //
T02TD1360E:156b-16: slob ma de ni gzung bar bya //
T02TD1360E:156b-17: de nas gsol ba gdab pa ni //
T02TD1360E:156b-18: skye ba mang po'i sdig pa ni //
T02TD1360E:156b-19: bsags pa rnam par 'jig byed pa //
T02TD1360E:156b-20: sdom pa so sor gzung bar bgyi //
T02TD1360E:156b-21: dpa' bo dus kyi 'khor lo brjod //
T02TD1360E:156b-22: de nas sa bslang brtag pa dang //
T02TD1360E:156b-23: sbyang dang gzung dang spel ba dang //
T02TD1360E:156b-24: dpyid 'bring dkar tshes nyam thar thug /
T02TD1360E:156b-25: gzhan la phan pa'i bla ma yis //
T02TD1360E:156b-26: sa brtag la sogs rim par bya //
T02TD1360E:156b-27: nags sam grong rdal khang stong sogs //
T02TD1360E:156b-28: byang dang dbang ldan phyogs su ni //
T02TD1360E:156b-29: dkar po zhi ba rgyas pa dang //
T02TD1360E:156b-30: sa la dri zhim dang ldan pa //
T02TD1360E:156b-31: sa dang chu ni brtags nas ni //
T02TD1360E:156b-32: bslang ba gnang dang mi gnang dang //
T02TD1360E:156b-33: sbyang ba pus mo lte ba dang //
T02TD1360E:156b-34: rked pa 'phang du brko bar bya //
T02TD1360E:156b-35: yang na rngo'am chur thug par //
T02TD1360E:156b-36: zug rdu sol ba bcas par ro //
T02TD1360E:156b-37: sa yi khong na yod pa ni //
T02TD1360E:156b-39: gnas de ru ni sbyang ba ni //
T02TD1360E:156b-40: yon tan gyi ni dbang gis 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:156b-41: de yi phyir na sbyang bar bya //
T02TD1360E:156b-42: nor bu mching bu dung yod na /
T02TD1360E:156b-43: rnam par rgyal zhing bde ba byed //
T02TD1360E:156b-44: dkyil 'khor sa gzhi'i don dang ni //
T02TD1360E:156b-45: khang bzangs don dang khyim don du //
T02TD1360E:156b-46: nges pa kho nar gsal ba ru //
T02TD1360E:156b-47: mchod sbyin la sogs rgyun sbyang bya //
T02TD1360E:156b-48: rdzogs pa la ni sbyang bya zhing //
T02TD1360E:156b-49: de bzhin sa ni gzung bar bya //
T02TD1360E:156b-50: bu rnams gzung ba la yang ngo //
T02TD1360E:156b-51: de yang shar dang byang du gzhol //
T02TD1360E:156b-52: dbus ni me long bzhin du mtho //
T02TD1360E:156b-53: brdung zhing legs par brdungs nas su //
T02TD1360E:156b-54: mnyam zhing zug rdu med par bya //
T02TD1360E:156b-55: der ni chu dang lci ba yis //
T02TD1360E:156b-56: dkyil 'khor sa ni legs par byug / de nas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis //
T02TD1360E:156b-57: gzung zhing bla re la sogs bri //
T02TD1360E:157a-2: nye snyid bzlas pas sa la reg / rdo rje yi ni rang bzhin bsam //
T02TD1360E:157a-3: lhag gnas yan lag cho ga'o //
T02TD1360E:157a-4: de nas dgongs ka'i dus su ni //
T02TD1360E:157a-5: chu dang mchod yon dri chab spos //
T02TD1360E:157a-6: me tog dang ni 'bras bu dang //
T02TD1360E:157a-7: bsang gtor dang ni mar ma dang //
T02TD1360E:157a-8: lha bshos gos dang bcur 'gyur te //
T02TD1360E:157a-9: dur khrod brgyad dang bcas pa yi //
T02TD1360E:157a-10: 'jig rten pa la gtor ma dang //
T02TD1360E:157a-11: sa yi lha mo'i mchod gtor dang //
T02TD1360E:157a-13: na bza' nyi shu rtsa lnga dang //
T02TD1360E:157a-14: bla re ba dan mandala dang //
T02TD1360E:157a-15: slob dpon rdzas brgyad ldan pa yis //
T02TD1360E:157a-16: yan lag bzhi pa'i sgrub thabs bzhin //
T02TD1360E:157a-17: rim pa bzhin du bsgoms nas ni //
T02TD1360E:157a-18: mandala steng gi dri thig le //
T02TD1360E:157a-19: me tog bkram la khro bo ni //
T02TD1360E:157a-20: 'dod pa'i rgyal po sa lha mo //
T02TD1360E:157a-21: ser mo phyag gnyis bum pa thogs //
T02TD1360E:157a-22: ro stod sa nas 'thon pa ni //
T02TD1360E:157a-23: bkug nas mchod yon zhabs bsil dbul //
T02TD1360E:157a-24: dam tshig phyag rgya brtan nas su //
T02TD1360E:157a-25: bstod dang gsol ba gdab par bya //
T02TD1360E:157a-26: lha yi dbang po lhan cig pa'i //
T02TD1360E:157a-27: bdud sde rgyal bas bcom pa yi //
T02TD1360E:157a-28: dpang por lha mo khyod ni gyur //
T02TD1360E:157a-29: de phyir khyod ni mchod par bya //
T02TD1360E:157a-30: lha yi mchog gis phyag byas pa //
T02TD1360E:157a-31: bdag gi mchod pa 'di bzhes shig / ji ltar rgyal bas byang chub phyir //
T02TD1360E:157a-32: bdud kyi sde ni mi bzad pa //
T02TD1360E:157a-33: stobs dang ldan pas bcom pa ltar //
T02TD1360E:157a-34: slob ma rnams ni dbang bskur phyir //
T02TD1360E:157a-35: de bzhin du ni bdag gis kyang //
T02TD1360E:157a-36: bdud kyi sde ni gzhom par bgyi //
T02TD1360E:157a-37: gang yang phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang //
T02TD1360E:157a-38: dri mdag dang bral ba yi //
T02TD1360E:157a-39: byang chub sems dpa' ma lus pa //
T02TD1360E:157a-40: de rnams nyid kyis bskyang bar mdzod //
T02TD1360E:157a-41: dkyil 'khor dbang bskur ba yi phyir //
T02TD1360E:157a-42: mchog gi snying rjes bskyang bar mdzod //
T02TD1360E:157a-43: de rnams kun la gsol btab nas //
T02TD1360E:157a-44: de nas rnam bcu'i mchod pa dang //
T02TD1360E:157a-45: gtong ma phul la gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1360E:157a-46: de nas sgrub pa'i grogs kyis su //
T02TD1360E:157a-47: rigs drug gi ni bstod pas bstod //
T02TD1360E:157a-48: seng ldeng mkhrang ba'i rang bzhin gyi //
T02TD1360E:157a-49: phur bu bdud rtsi 'khyil par bskyed //
T02TD1360E:157a-50: skud gdags phur pa'i gsang sngags bzlas //
T02TD1360E:157a-51: de nas sngags dang phyag rgya yis //
T02TD1360E:157a-52: dkyil 'khor snying gar bsdu bar bya //
T02TD1360E:157a-53: rkang gnyis h'um las rdo rje dang //
T02TD1360E:157b-0: @157b mig tu nyi ma zla ba bsam //
T02TD1360E:157b-2: khro bo'i dbyangs kyis bstod pa bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-3: de nas bgegs la bka' bsgo bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-4: gsang ba'i rgyud las 'byung ba yi //
T02TD1360E:157b-5: stang stabs ji tsam nus pa bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-6: de nas bsrung ba'i 'khor lo ni //
T02TD1360E:157b-7: dpal kye rdo rje phyogs kun nas ;
T02TD1360E:157b-8: / gnas pa yi ni bdud kyi tshogs //
T02TD1360E:157b-9: ma lus pa ni nges par bsreg / rdo rje gsum gyi ra ba gsum //
T02TD1360E:157b-10: sa yis 'khor bar song ba yi //
T02TD1360E:157b-11: sa 'og gnas dang nam mkhar ro //
T02TD1360E:157b-12: rdo rje khang pa brtsegs ma yin //
T02TD1360E:157b-13: dbus su 'dam skyes nyi ma'i khru //
T02TD1360E:157b-14: lte ba dang ldan gdan la ni //
T02TD1360E:157b-15: dus dang lag pa'i khru ru 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:157b-16: de yi steng du bdag nyid ni //
T02TD1360E:157b-17: dre ma dang ni bral ba nyid //
T02TD1360E:157b-18: 'khor lo'i dbus su khro dbang po //
T02TD1360E:157b-19: phyag ni rgyal ba gnyis lhag pa //
T02TD1360E:157b-20: dus kyi zhal te rdo rje'i shugs //
T02TD1360E:157b-21: rnal 'byor pa yis bsgom par bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-22: phyi nas 'khor lo rtsibs bcu pa //
T02TD1360E:157b-23: phyogs dang mtshams su song ba yi //
T02TD1360E:157b-24: khro mo'i tshogs ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-25: de nas sngar gyi phur bu ni //
T02TD1360E:157b-26: sngags kyis phyogs mtshams steng 'og gdab //
T02TD1360E:157b-27: de la dri dang bdug pa bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-29: de nas dri yi chu dang ni //
T02TD1360E:157b-30: ba yi rnam lnga'i skyang nul bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-31: thig le nyi shu rtsa lnga dang //
T02TD1360E:157b-32: me tog tshom yang de mnyam bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-33: de nas rang gnas lha gnas pa'i //
T02TD1360E:157b-34: rnal 'byor pas ni snying ga nas //
T02TD1360E:157b-35: dkyil 'khor la ni sprul par bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-36: de nas de la cho ga dang //
T02TD1360E:157b-37: ye shes spyan drangs mchod bstod bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-38: dbang bskur nas de dgug gzhug bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-39: de nas chang dang bdud rtsi dang //
T02TD1360E:157b-40: mchod pa rnam pa bcu po dang //
T02TD1360E:157b-41: bstod pa rnam pa du ma dang ;
T02TD1360E:157b-42: / na bza' ci 'byor dbul bar bya //
T02TD1360E:157b-43: go cha'i sngags kyis bsrungs nas ni //
T02TD1360E:157b-44: gnyis med ye shes las byung ba /
T02TD1360E:157b-45: khyab bdag brtan g-yo'i bdag po ni //
T02TD1360E:157b-46: bcom ldan dus kyi 'khor lo gtso //
T02TD1360E:157b-47: sna tshogs yum gyis mgul nas 'khyud //
T02TD1360E:157b-48: nyi shu rtsa lnga pa yi 'khor //
T02TD1360E:157b-49: ma lus bdag la dgongs su gsol //
T02TD1360E:157b-50: slob ma rnams la phan pa dang //
T02TD1360E:157b-51: khyed rnams la yang mchod pa'i phyir //
T02TD1360E:157b-52: rdo rje can bdag 'di zhes pa'i //
T02TD1360E:157b-53: nang par dkyil 'khor bri bar bgyi //
T02TD1360E:157b-54: rjes su brtse bar nyer dgongs te //
T02TD1360E:157b-55: kun gyis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
T02TD1360E:157b-56: de ltar lha ni lhag byas nas //
T02TD1360E:158a-2: de yang rnam rgyal bum pa ni //
T02TD1360E:158a-3: rgya ru brgyad gnyis so sor gsum pa //
T02TD1360E:158a-4: dpangs su sor tshad bcu phrag gnyis //
T02TD1360E:158a-5: mchu ni sor gnyis ske sor drug / shel lam dngul gyi bum pa ni //
T02TD1360E:158a-6: ri bong 'dzin pa ltar dkar ba //
T02TD1360E:158a-7: yang na tha mal bum pa ni //
T02TD1360E:158a-8: 'bras la sogs pas kha dog bsgyur //
T02TD1360E:158a-9: bum pa rnam pa bcu la ni //
T02TD1360E:158a-10: rigs kyi mtshan ma rnams bkod la //
T02TD1360E:158a-11: sman dang 'bru rnams gzhug pa ni //
T02TD1360E:158a-12: dri yi sman gyi re mig tu //
T02TD1360E:158a-13: rim pa bzhin du sman gyi grangs //
T02TD1360E:158a-14: mig dang zla ba la sogs chas //
T02TD1360E:158a-15: tshangs ma la sogs lnga lnga la //
T02TD1360E:158a-16: tshangs ma khyab 'jug ma drag mo //
T02TD1360E:158a-17: dbang phyug ma dang dbang chen mo //
T02TD1360E:158a-18: dpang mo dpal mo phag mo dang //
T02TD1360E:158a-19: gzhon nu ma dang rgan byad ma //
T02TD1360E:158a-20: sa mo chu mo me mo dang //
T02TD1360E:158a-21: rlung mo mkha' spyod ma de bzhin //
T02TD1360E:158a-22: ma dang sring mo bu mo dang //
T02TD1360E:158a-23: tsha mo rang rmongs ma de bzhin //
T02TD1360E:158a-24: bram ze mo dang rgyal rigs mo //
T02TD1360E:158a-25: rje'u rigs mo dang dmangs rigs mo //
T02TD1360E:158a-26: g-yung mo de bzhin shes bar bya //
T02TD1360E:158a-27: sman 'di yis ni dngos grub che //
T02TD1360E:158a-28: spyod dang grol ba rab tu ster //
T02TD1360E:158a-30: mon sran dkar dang tsanda na dkar //
T02TD1360E:158a-31: til nag lnga pa dang po yin //
T02TD1360E:158a-32: kro tra 'bras sngon sran ma dang //
T02TD1360E:158a-33: til dkar gro ni gnyis pa yin ;
T02TD1360E:158a-34: / mu tra yu tri pu yungs smug / nas sran ma sha gsum pa yin //
T02TD1360E:158a-35: sran chung yungs kar dkar po dang //
T02TD1360E:158a-36: ka kun tri bi ka ra dang /
T02TD1360E:158a-37: ba ra tsi ka bzhi pa yin //
T02TD1360E:158a-38: aa ta shi dang par ti //
T02TD1360E:158a-39: ba la rgya sran tsandan nag //
T02TD1360E:158a-40: de ni lnga par bkod pa yin //
T02TD1360E:158a-41: de nas rin po che yi rigs //
T02TD1360E:158a-42: bram ze rgyal dang rje dmangs dang //
T02TD1360E:158a-43: mthar skyes rigs kyi rdo rje'o //
T02TD1360E:158a-44: de nas aindra bar ka / chu shel ke ke ru ma rgad //
T02TD1360E:158a-45: dang po'i lnga tshan bstan ba yin //
T02TD1360E:158a-46: lcags dang gser dngul zangs khro chu //
T02TD1360E:158a-47: khab len lnga tshan gnyis pa yin //
T02TD1360E:158a-48: mu tig byu ru mthing shing dang //
T02TD1360E:158a-49: ka sha ma ni shad aa ru //
T02TD1360E:158a-50: lnga tshan gsum par bkod pa yin //
T02TD1360E:158a-51: yu dza dza pa dz'a ti dang //
T02TD1360E:158a-52: do ba ri ga 'ba' ha ri ta //
T02TD1360E:158a-53: lnga tshan bzhi par bkod pa yin //
T02TD1360E:158a-54: lnga pa 'khor los sgyur ba yin //
T02TD1360E:158a-55: lha klu'i nor bu kha dog lnga'o //
T02TD1360E:158a-56: 'byor ba med na kha dog lnga //
T02TD1360E:158a-57: me tog lnga ni gzhug par bya //
T02TD1360E:158b-0: ljang gu rnam rgyal bum par gzhug / sngon po @158b rgyal dang rnam rgyal la //
T02TD1360E:158b-1: nag po shar me'i bum par ro //
T02TD1360E:158b-2: dmar po lho dang bden bral lo //
T02TD1360E:158b-3: dkar po byang dang dbang ldan du'o //
T02TD1360E:158b-4: ser po nub dang rlung du'o //
T02TD1360E:158b-5: thams cad cha dbyes bcug nas ni //
T02TD1360E:158b-6: rigs mthun gos kyis mgrin pa bcing //
T02TD1360E:158b-7: g-yas su padma'i steng bzhag nas /
T02TD1360E:158b-8: sh'u n+ya t'a yis stong par bsam //
T02TD1360E:158b-9: de nas ham las gzhal yas khang //
T02TD1360E:158b-10: bam las 'o ma'i rgya mtsho bskyed //
T02TD1360E:158b-12: h'um las lha rnams bskyed par bya //
T02TD1360E:158b-13: cho ga gong ma 'dra ba las //
T02TD1360E:158b-14: nag por shar gyi lha tshogs bskyed //
T02TD1360E:158b-15: gzhan yang de bzhin shes par bya //
T02TD1360E:158b-16: de nas bgegs bskrad ye shes dgug / dbang bskur yig gsum byin brlabs la //
T02TD1360E:158b-17: mchod bstod gong ma bzhin du bya //
T02TD1360E:158b-18: tshon skud bum pa'i steng bzhag nas //
T02TD1360E:158b-19: thun gcig par du bzlas par bya //
T02TD1360E:158b-20: de nas bum pa bsdus nas su //
T02TD1360E:158b-21: gos kyis bkab nas zhal bzhis bsrung //
T02TD1360E:158b-22: de ltar bum pa lhag gnas nas //
T02TD1360E:158b-23: sbyin sreg lhag par gnas par bya //
T02TD1360E:158b-24: grong khyer gyi ni dbus nyid dang //
T02TD1360E:158b-25: byang dang dbang ldan mtshams su'o //
T02TD1360E:158b-26: thag khung khru gang zlum po la //
T02TD1360E:158b-27: zabs su khru phyed brko bar bya //
T02TD1360E:158b-28: mchu ni thab khung bcu gnyis cha //
T02TD1360E:158b-29: de yi nyis 'gyur kha khyer ro //
T02TD1360E:158b-30: kha khyer dpangs la mchu yi phyed //
T02TD1360E:158b-32: tshon rtsi dkar pos bri bar bya //
T02TD1360E:158b-34: ku sha yis ni dgram par bya //
T02TD1360E:158b-35: de yi mtha' yi nub tu ni //
T02TD1360E:158b-36: nges pa kho nar bya ba ni //
T02TD1360E:158b-37: rab gsum la sgo gcig pa //
T02TD1360E:158b-38: slob dpon gyi ni bdag nyid ni //
T02TD1360E:158b-39: mnyam pa kho nar bya ba yin //
T02TD1360E:158b-40: sngar gsungs mchod pa bcu pa ni //
T02TD1360E:158b-41: rim pa bzhin du bsham par bya //
T02TD1360E:158b-42: n+ya gro dha dang 'o ma can //
T02TD1360E:158b-43: bsreg pa'i shing ni mda' yi brgya //

T02TD1360E:161a-49: dus dang de bzhin ro yis ni ;
T02TD1360E:161a-50: / sgo dang sgo khyud de bzhin du //
T02TD1360E:161a-51: sor phyed drug las 'gram dang logs //
T02TD1360E:161a-52: kha khyer chen po ka ba'i phyed //
T02TD1360E:161a-53: de yi phyed kyis nor bu yi //
T02TD1360E:161a-55: nyis 'gyur dra ba dra phyed ba //
T02TD1360E:161a-56: sgo yi rtsa ba'i phyi rol du //
T02TD1360E:161a-57: sor phyed drug gi sum 'gyur gyis //
T02TD1360E:161b-0: ka bar bcas pa'i @161b rta babs 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:161b-1: thig las mtha' ru spang bar bya //
T02TD1360E:161b-2: de yi phyi rol 'byung ba bzhi //
T02TD1360E:161b-3: yang ni spros don ma yin pa //
T02TD1360E:161b-4: gcig bzhi gnyis bzhi gcig nyi ma //
T02TD1360E:161b-5: dus dang ro dang rtse mo can //
T02TD1360E:161b-6: me dang dus dang dus kyi phyed //
T02TD1360E:161b-7: dus la drug gi rab phyed dang //
T02TD1360E:161b-8: dus drug dang ni ro rnams kyi //
T02TD1360E:161b-9: nges par cha yi rim pa yis //
T02TD1360E:161b-10: lte ba'am ni snying po nas //
T02TD1360E:161b-11: chu skyes padma yang de ni //
T02TD1360E:161b-12: ka ba rdo rje phreng ba dang //
T02TD1360E:161b-14: sgo dang sgo khyud la sogs pa'i //
T02TD1360E:161b-16: ka bar ba kha khyer dang //
T02TD1360E:161b-17: slar la yang ni de 'og tu //
T02TD1360E:161b-18: pha gu dra ba dra phyed pa //
T02TD1360E:161b-19: me long la sogs snam bu sa //
T02TD1360E:161b-20: mi yi bdag por gyur ba dang //
T02TD1360E:161b-21: rta babs kyi ni cha rab gsungs //
T02TD1360E:161b-22: de ltar thig gi las zin nas //
T02TD1360E:161b-23: tshon gyi las ni rab tu bya //
T02TD1360E:161b-24: rdo rje la sogs rdul tshon lnga //
T02TD1360E:161b-25: gser dang padma r'a ga dang //
T02TD1360E:161b-26: byu ru mu tig la sogs pa //
T02TD1360E:161b-27: 'bru yi khyad par dag dang ni //
T02TD1360E:161b-28: nor bu'i khyad par mang po yi //
T02TD1360E:161b-29: phye ma rdul tshon de bzhin du ;
T02TD1360E:161b-30: / thig bzhin byin rlabs chog bya //
T02TD1360E:161b-31: phyogs kyi cha yi tshon gyi sar //
T02TD1360E:161b-32: mi yi bdag po rdul tshon gyi //
T02TD1360E:161b-33: sangs rgyas dbye bas bri bar bya //
T02TD1360E:161b-34: ser po dkar bo dmar sogs kyis //
T02TD1360E:161b-35: sa dang chu dang me rlung ni //
T02TD1360E:161b-36: rim pa bzhin du bri bar bya //
T02TD1360E:161b-37: shar gyis ni dpal nag go //
T02TD1360E:161b-38: nyi ma lta bur lho ru'o //
T02TD1360E:161b-39: nub tu gser du snang ba ste //
T02TD1360E:161b-40: byang du ri bong 'dzin dkar po //
T02TD1360E:161b-41: rdo rje 'dzin zhal dbye bas so //
T02TD1360E:161b-42: dkar po dmar po nag po'o //
T02TD1360E:161b-43: rim pas yongs su bris nas so //
T02TD1360E:161b-44: kha khyer pha gu dra ba'i sa //
T02TD1360E:161b-45: padma zla ba nyi ma'i mdog / dri med ri bong can 'dra dang //
T02TD1360E:161b-46: dmar po nag po ne kh'a gsum //
T02TD1360E:161b-48: ljang gu a'a li lta bu'o //
T02TD1360E:161b-49: ka ba rdo rje phreng bar 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:161b-50: dbang ldan bden bral me rlung du //
T02TD1360E:161b-51: zla ba nyi ma dag gi mdog / nag po ser po dmar po yis //
T02TD1360E:161b-52: dung dang gand'i nor bu dang //
T02TD1360E:161b-53: ljon shing dang ni de bzhin du //
T02TD1360E:161b-54: bum pa dkar po padma yi //
T02TD1360E:161b-55: steng du zla ba dmar po ni //
T02TD1360E:161b-56: 'gyur ro nyin mor byed pa ni //
T02TD1360E:161b-58: padma dkar po'i lte bar lha //
T02TD1360E:161b-59: ri bong 'dzin pa'i gdan la ni //
T02TD1360E:161b-60: lha mo rnams ni gnas par 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:161b-61: padma dkar po'i lte ba la //
T02TD1360E:161b-62: nyin mor byed pa dgod pa yi //
T02TD1360E:161b-63: lha rnams phyogs su gnas pa na //
T02TD1360E:161b-64: phyi ru rdo rje phreng bar 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:162a-2: kha khyer dag ni mdog dkar po //
T02TD1360E:162a-3: ba ku li dang ka ba ni //
T02TD1360E:162a-5: rta babs kha dog sna tshogs so //
T02TD1360E:162a-6: sbom pos nad ni skyed par byed //
T02TD1360E:162a-7: phra mos nges pa kho nar ni //
T02TD1360E:162a-8: nor nyams mtshan ngan ri mo spang //
T02TD1360E:162a-9: chad pas 'chi zhing yon po yis //
T02TD1360E:162a-10: mi rnams skye bo'i bdag pos skrod //
T02TD1360E:162a-11: de bzhin mtshan ma nyi ma'i bdag / srid pa yi ni 'jigs 'joms la //
T02TD1360E:162a-12: sngags pa rnams ni dngos grub med //
T02TD1360E:162a-14: rgyal rigs dkyil 'khor la ni bya //
T02TD1360E:162a-15: rgyal ba nges pa kho nar ster //
T02TD1360E:162a-16: rgyud kyi nang du gang ma gsungs //
T02TD1360E:162a-17: mtshan ma mdzes pa'i ched du ni //
T02TD1360E:162a-18: dkyil 'khor du ni de mi dgod //
T02TD1360E:162a-19: rgyal bas rigs ni shes med pas //
T02TD1360E:162a-20: de nyid bdud kyi mtshan ma'o //
T02TD1360E:162a-21: de phyir rgyud gsungs mtshan ma ni //
T02TD1360E:162a-22: rigs kyi dbang gis bya bar 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:162a-23: dkyil 'khor sgo yi bar du ni //
T02TD1360E:162a-24: dra ba dra phyed bar de bya //
T02TD1360E:162a-25: sa dang rlung gi dkyil 'khor la //
T02TD1360E:162a-26: padma bum pa sogs byis brgyan //
T02TD1360E:162a-27: nag po la sogs rdul tshon rnams //
T02TD1360E:162a-29: nas gcig par du mtho ba'o //
T02TD1360E:162a-31: nyin mor byed dang ri bong can //
T02TD1360E:162a-32: re kh'a gzhan ni nyis 'gyur te //
T02TD1360E:162a-34: mi yi bdag por 'gyur ba yin //
T02TD1360E:162a-35: dra ba dra phyed mthar thug dang //
T02TD1360E:162a-36: sa dang chu dang byin za dang //
T02TD1360E:162a-37: phyi rol rdo rje'i phreng gnas gcig / aom gyi ye shes las skyes par //
T02TD1360E:162a-38: rgyal ba dam pa'i padma yi //
T02TD1360E:162a-39: nyi ma zla ba'i gdan stengs su //
T02TD1360E:162a-40: aa sogs ka sogs stong bar bcas //
T02TD1360E:162a-41: srid pa gsum ni bskyed pa yi //
T02TD1360E:162a-42: yum ni gzhag par bya ba yin //
T02TD1360E:162a-43: stong ba aa dang tsheg drag dang //
T02TD1360E:162a-44: gzhan ni dbyangs dang bral ba'o //
T02TD1360E:162a-45: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje ni //
T02TD1360E:162a-46: yang dag 'byung phyir sngags skye gnas //
T02TD1360E:162a-47: mchog tu bde ba byed pa yi //
T02TD1360E:162a-48: ye shes rdo rje bzhi pa'o //
T02TD1360E:162a-49: h'um ni kha dog sna tshogs pa //
T02TD1360E:162a-50: rgyal po'i bdag po'i padma yi //
T02TD1360E:162a-51: zla ba nyi ma me steng du //
T02TD1360E:162a-52: dbang ldan bden bral gyi ni mtshams //
T02TD1360E:162a-53: rtse mo can dang rlung du ni //
T02TD1360E:162a-54: sku dang gsung dang thugs chags pas //
T02TD1360E:162a-55: ham sogs bum pa brgyad kyi'o //
T02TD1360E:162a-56: shar gyi padmar ai yig ste //
T02TD1360E:162a-57: me yi padma ru song ba //
T02TD1360E:162a-58: yi ge a'i ni ring po nyid //
T02TD1360E:162a-59: gshin rje bden bral ri yig gnyis //
T02TD1360E:162b-0: shar dang @162b nor sbyin phyogs song ba //
T02TD1360E:162b-1: thung dang ring ba'i au yig go //
T02TD1360E:162b-2: chu dang rlung gi mtshams su ni //
T02TD1360E:162b-3: gzhan yang padma ru song ba //
T02TD1360E:162b-4: thung dang ring ba'i li yig go //
T02TD1360E:162b-5: nag po dmar po dkar po dang //
T02TD1360E:162b-6: gser ni btso ma lta bu ni //
T02TD1360E:162b-7: zhal gyi dbye ba yod pa yis //
T02TD1360E:162b-8: shar gyi sgo yi g-yas dang ni //
T02TD1360E:162b-9: rtse mo can gyi pad song ba //
T02TD1360E:162b-10: ring dang thung bde bzhin nyid //
T02TD1360E:162b-11: gshin rje ru ni bden bral du //
T02TD1360E:162b-12: de bzhin du ni aa ra ni zung //
T02TD1360E:162b-13: nub dang rlung du a'a la ni zung //
T02TD1360E:162b-15: lha dang chu lha gshin rje yi //
T02TD1360E:162b-16: sgo yi g-yon dang gnod sbyin bcas //
T02TD1360E:162b-17: aam dang aa yi rim pa yis //
T02TD1360E:162b-18: gzhan yang ya ra wa la dang //
T02TD1360E:162b-19: sgo yi padmar rlung la sogs //
T02TD1360E:162b-20: shar gyi sgo dang g-yas min par //
T02TD1360E:162b-21: khro bo dag gi gdan du ni //
T02TD1360E:162b-23: g-yas dang nub tu nyi ma yang //
T02TD1360E:162b-24: padma dag gi steng du ni //
T02TD1360E:162b-25: gdan gnyis dag tu rab tu 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:162b-26: shes rab thabs kyi rab dbye bas //
T02TD1360E:162b-27: padma'i steng du zla ba dang //
T02TD1360E:162b-28: nyi ma yang ni gdan du 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:162b-29: g-yas dang rgyab tu nyi mar 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:162b-30: lha yi bdag por gnod sbyin du //
T02TD1360E:162b-31: zla ba yi ni gdan du 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:162b-32: thung dang ring po'i sde tshan drug / rang bzhin yon tan dbang gis na //
T02TD1360E:162b-33: kha khyer ka ba'i logs su'o //
T02TD1360E:162b-34: dri sogs rnams ni rim pa bzhin //
T02TD1360E:162b-35: rang gi rigs kyi sar song ba //
T02TD1360E:162b-36: shar gyi cha nas rang phyogs su'o //
T02TD1360E:162b-37: de ltar bris pa zin pa dang //
T02TD1360E:162b-38: de nas rdzas rnams bsag par bya //
T02TD1360E:162b-39: rdo rje dril bu la sogs pa //
T02TD1360E:162b-40: slob dpon gyi ni rdzas rnams dang //
T02TD1360E:162b-41: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan la sogs pa //
T02TD1360E:162b-42: dkyil 'khor gyi ni rdzas rnams dang ;
T02TD1360E:162b-43: / de rjes mchod pa'i yan lag rdzas //
T02TD1360E:162b-44: re re nyi shu rtsa lnga dang //
T02TD1360E:162b-45: khyad par tshogs kyi mchod pa'i rdzas //
T02TD1360E:162b-46: chang dbang bdud rtsi la sogs pa //
T02TD1360E:162b-47: ci 'byor ba ni bsags par byas //
T02TD1360E:162b-48: bsrung ba mda' dang phur bu dang //
T02TD1360E:162b-49: yungs kar phur bu tshon skud do //
T02TD1360E:162b-50: sgrub pa bum pa rnams dang yang //
T02TD1360E:162b-51: sbyin sreg rdzas dang gtor ma'o //
T02TD1360E:162b-52: bsod nams bsog pa'i rdzas dag ni //
T02TD1360E:162b-53: rin chen bdun dang rdzas brgyad dang //
T02TD1360E:162b-55: 'dod pa'i yon tan rnam pa lnga'o //
T02TD1360E:162b-57: de nas dgongs kyi dus su ni //
T02TD1360E:162b-58: dkyil 'khor sngags kyis bslang byas la //
T02TD1360E:163a-2: lha rnams ma lus tshang bar bsgom //
T02TD1360E:163a-3: de nas shar du las kyi ni //
T02TD1360E:163a-4: he ru ka yi gzugs kyis dbye //
T02TD1360E:163a-5: tsham dam sngags kyis bstod pa dang //
T02TD1360E:163a-7: bgegs bskrad lhag dang mtshang bskang //
T02TD1360E:163a-8: lha la me tog phreng ba dor //
T02TD1360E:163a-9: sngags kyi mtshan ma khang pa'i nang //
T02TD1360E:163a-10: shel gyi bum pa dkar po la //
T02TD1360E:163a-11: skud pa sna lngas dkris pa ni //
T02TD1360E:163a-12: zur du yang dag gzhag par bya //
T02TD1360E:163a-13: slob dpon 'khor lo'i shar du ni //
T02TD1360E:163a-14: gnas nas sdig pa bshags sogs dang //
T02TD1360E:163a-15: dkyil 'khor rgyal po mchog dang ni //
T02TD1360E:163a-16: las kyi rgyal po'i mchog la ni //
T02TD1360E:163a-17: rigs gtso padma las skyes pa'i //
T02TD1360E:163a-18: byung ba khro bo'i rgyal po yis //
T02TD1360E:163a-19: ye shes 'khor lo bkug nas ni //
T02TD1360E:163a-20: mchod yon dang ni mchod pa bcu //
T02TD1360E:163a-21: lha rnams kun la rgyas byas la //
T02TD1360E:163a-22: dza: h'um bam ho: lcags kyu sogs //
T02TD1360E:163a-23: rim bzhin yongs su bskyed pa yis //
T02TD1360E:163a-24: dgug gzhug bcing dang dgyes byas nas //
T02TD1360E:163a-25: rdul tshon dang ni ro mnyam pa //
T02TD1360E:163a-26: dbang gi ched du bya ba yin //
T02TD1360E:163a-27: de nas bum pa thams cad la //
T02TD1360E:163a-28: bzlas pa lha re brgya byas la //
T02TD1360E:163a-29: mchod dang lha rnams zhu bar bya //
T02TD1360E:163a-30: zhu ba'i chu yis dkyil 'khor la //
T02TD1360E:163a-31: dbang bskur rim pa bzhin byas la //
T02TD1360E:163a-32: de nas bdud rtsi lnga rnams ni //
T02TD1360E:163a-33: lha rnams sngags kyis dbul bar bya //
T02TD1360E:163a-34: h'um yig ye shes sa bon ni //
T02TD1360E:163a-35: snying po yang ni chen po ste //
T02TD1360E:163a-36: brtsegs pa'i yi ge gzhal du bcas //
T02TD1360E:163a-37: ham la sogs pa go cha drug / nye ba yi ni snying po 'di //
T02TD1360E:163a-38: sku yi rdo rje dang por ldan //
T02TD1360E:163a-39: phreng ba'i sngags ni de bzhin gzhan //
T02TD1360E:163a-40: las kyi dbye ba du ma yis //
T02TD1360E:163a-41: rnam pa mang po ru ni 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:163a-42: de bzhin 'khor gyi sngags kyis kyang //
T02TD1360E:163a-43: bdud rtsi lnga ni dbul ba yin //
T02TD1360E:163a-44: de nas gong gsungs sreg blugs kyis //
T02TD1360E:163a-45: lha rnams kun la sbyin sreg sbyin //
T02TD1360E:163a-46: de nas mchod pa thams cad ni //
T02TD1360E:163a-47: dbyangs dang bstod sgra ldan pas ni //
T02TD1360E:163a-48: rin chen gser dang chu me tog / rnam pa sna tshogs pa dang ras //
T02TD1360E:163a-49: dri dang spos dang mar me dang //
T02TD1360E:163a-50: dril bu me long bla re dang //
T02TD1360E:163a-51: 'bras bu sna tshogs pa la sogs //
T02TD1360E:163a-52: gar dang rol mo la sogs pa'i //
T02TD1360E:163a-53: mchod pa sna tshogs byas nas ni //
T02TD1360E:163a-54: gong gi gtor ma rgya chen sbyin //
T02TD1360E:163b-0: de ltar mchod pa'i @163b las zin nas //
T02TD1360E:163b-1: de nas slob ma gzhug pa ni //
T02TD1360E:163b-2: khrus dang dri yis rjes byugs shing //
T02TD1360E:163b-3: lus la gos ni ser byin te //
T02TD1360E:163b-4: mig ni dar gyis bkab nas su //
T02TD1360E:163b-5: yol ba'i rgyab tu bzhag nas ni //
T02TD1360E:163b-6: bsang chu dang ni dris lan bya //
T02TD1360E:163b-7: rgyal rnams la ni deng bdag nyid //
T02TD1360E:163b-9: / sku dang gsung dang thugs dag pa //
T02TD1360E:163b-10: srid pa yi ni 'jigs sel ba //
T02TD1360E:163b-11: khyed kyi zhabs kyi padma ru //
T02TD1360E:163b-12: skyabs su lhag par 'gro bar bgyi //
T02TD1360E:163b-13: gser dang bcas pa'i me tog gis //
T02TD1360E:163b-14: mandala dag ni byas pa yin //
T02TD1360E:163b-15: de ltar gsol ba btab nas ni //
T02TD1360E:163b-16: yol ba'i nang du bsdu bar bya //
T02TD1360E:163b-17: byin gyis brlabs pa'i phyag bzhi dang //
T02TD1360E:163b-18: bdun po rnams dag rdzogs par bya //
T02TD1360E:163b-19: de nas smon lam gdab pa ni //
T02TD1360E:163b-20: rdo rje dril bu phyag rgya dang //
T02TD1360E:163b-21: bla ma yang ni spyi bo ru //
T02TD1360E:163b-23: rin chen gyi ni sbyin pa sbyin //
T02TD1360E:163b-24: rgyal pa mchog gi dam tshig ni //
T02TD1360E:163b-26: ral gri yis ni mchod par bya //
T02TD1360E:163b-27: chu las skyes kyi rigs kyi ni //
T02TD1360E:163b-28: sdom pa yang ni bskyang bar bgyi //
T02TD1360E:163b-29: sems can rnams ni grol ba'i rgyur //
T02TD1360E:163b-30: rgyal bskyed byed rigs kyi ni //
T02TD1360E:163b-31: byang chub dag ni bskyed par bgyi //
T02TD1360E:163b-32: de nas dam tshig rdo rje sbyin //
T02TD1360E:163b-33: snying ga yi ni zla ba la //
T02TD1360E:163b-34: h'um las rdo rje bkod nas ni //
T02TD1360E:163b-35: byang chub sems ni bskyed par bgyi //
T02TD1360E:163b-36: de nas lha dang slob dpon gyi //
T02TD1360E:163b-37: dam tshig rab tu bsgrag par bya //
T02TD1360E:163b-38: lce la rgyal ba mchog gi ni //
T02TD1360E:163b-39: dam tshig gi ni bdud rtsi bzhin //
T02TD1360E:163b-40: sbos ni dbab pa'i don du'o //
T02TD1360E:163b-41: h'um gi sngags ni gcig pu dang //
T02TD1360E:163b-42: aa ra la dang lhan cig tu //
T02TD1360E:163b-43: khro bo yi ni rgyal ba bskul //
T02TD1360E:163b-44: de yi mtshan nyid rgyud na gsal //
T02TD1360E:163b-45: dbab pa padma'i steng la ni //
T02TD1360E:163b-46: spyi bo snying ga spyi gtsug dang //
T02TD1360E:163b-47: lte ba mgrin pa gsang ba ru //
T02TD1360E:163b-48: rgyal ba rigs kyi sar son pa //
T02TD1360E:163b-49: rdo rje gsum gyis bsrub pa bya //
T02TD1360E:163b-50: de nas rigs ni dag bya'i phyir //
T02TD1360E:163b-51: aom sarba zhes bya ba yi //
T02TD1360E:163b-52: dpal kyi sngags kyis mngon bsngags te //
T02TD1360E:163b-53: lag pa'i padma sbyar byas la //
T02TD1360E:163b-54: me tog gcig ni rab tu sbyin //
T02TD1360E:163b-55: dang po bskor ba gsum byas te //
T02TD1360E:163b-56: lag pa'i padmo sbyor byas pa'i //
T02TD1360E:163b-57: me tog dkyil 'khor du ni dor //
T02TD1360E:163b-58: gnas gang du ni lhung ba ni //
T02TD1360E:163b-59: de yis rigs so'i mi bdag kye //
T02TD1360E:163b-60: dbye ba'i sngags kyis mig ni dbye //
T02TD1360E:164a-2: gtso bo la sogs pa ni bstan //
T02TD1360E:164a-3: 'jug pa bdun ni mi'i bdag go //
T02TD1360E:164a-4: de nas dbang bskur bya ba ni //
T02TD1360E:164a-5: slob ma shar gyis ru ni //
T02TD1360E:164a-6: cho ga bzhin du lhar bskyed nas //
T02TD1360E:164a-7: rigs ni dag par byas nas ni //
T02TD1360E:164a-8: de nas byang gi sgo ru ni //
T02TD1360E:164a-9: rgyal po klu dang bzhi yis te //
T02TD1360E:164a-10: rgyal dang rnam rgyal bum pa dang //
T02TD1360E:164a-11: lha mo rnams kyis bkrus pa ni //
T02TD1360E:164a-12: sgrol ma la sogs pa ru 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:164a-13: cod pan sangs rgyas rab dbye bas //
T02TD1360E:164a-14: bla ma mchog gis sbyin par bya //
T02TD1360E:164a-15: de ltar sku ni dag byas la //
T02TD1360E:164a-16: lho ru gsung ni dag par bya //
T02TD1360E:164a-17: dar dbyangs nus pa rnams yin no //
T02TD1360E:164a-18: rdo rje dril bu nyi zla dag /
T02TD1360E:164a-19: de nas shar du brtul zhugs ni //
T02TD1360E:164a-20: dbang po rnams la sbyar ba'o //
T02TD1360E:164a-21: ming ni khro bo byams sogs dag / der ni nub kyi sgo du ni //
T02TD1360E:164a-22: rgyal ba'i bdag pos nges par ni //
T02TD1360E:164a-23: sngags dang bcas pa'i gnang ba sbyin //
T02TD1360E:164a-24: rdo rje dril bu rab sbyin te //
T02TD1360E:164a-25: rab mchog gi ni snying rje yis //
T02TD1360E:164a-26: dag pa'i chos ni bstan par bya ;
T02TD1360E:164a-27: / rigs gtso rigs kyi nges par ni //
T02TD1360E:164a-28: srog bcad pa ni bya ba yin //
T02TD1360E:164a-29: ral gri mi bden bar smra ba'i //
T02TD1360E:164a-30: rin po che yis gzhan nor dbrog / padmas gzhan gyi bud med dbrog / chang dang mar me sangs rgyas dang //
T02TD1360E:164a-31: yul ni du ma ma lus dang //
T02TD1360E:164a-32: 'khor lo yis ni bsten par bya //
T02TD1360E:164a-33: gri gug g-yung sogs bud med kyi //
T02TD1360E:164a-34: mkha' yi padma smad mi bya //
T02TD1360E:164a-35: sems can rnams kyi don gyi phyir //
T02TD1360E:164a-36: nor bcas lus ni sbyin par bya'o //
T02TD1360E:164a-37: khyod kyis zhen par mi bya'o //
T02TD1360E:164a-38: bskal ba dpag med rgyal bas gsungs //
T02TD1360E:164a-39: sangs rgyas nyid de gzhan du min //
T02TD1360E:164a-40: min par 'gyur ro rigs kyi bu //
T02TD1360E:164a-41: chu ni sgrol ma sogs lha mo //
T02TD1360E:164a-42: cod pan 'dir ni rgyal ba rnams //
T02TD1360E:164a-43: dar dbyangs nus pa rnams yin no //
T02TD1360E:164a-44: rdo rje nor bu nyi ma zla //
T02TD1360E:164a-45: brtul zhugs yul ni dag par 'dod //
T02TD1360E:164a-46: ming ni byams pas sogs la sbyor //
T02TD1360E:164a-47: gnang ba rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob //
T02TD1360E:164a-48: srid pa yi ni 'jigs pa sel //
T02TD1360E:164a-49: dus kyi 'khor lo rdo rjes shes pa'o //
T02TD1360E:164a-50: 'di dag dbang ni bdun yin no //
T02TD1360E:164a-51: nyon mongs dri ma sel bar byed //
T02TD1360E:164a-52: dkyil 'khor du ni rab sbyin bya //
T02TD1360E:164a-53: dbang bdun bskur bas sa bdun gyi //
T02TD1360E:164a-54: dbang phyug tu ni grol bar 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:164a-55: bum pa gsang ba'i dbang bskur bas //
T02TD1360E:164a-56: yang ni phyir mi ldog pa sogs //
T02TD1360E:164a-57: nges pa kho nar 'jug par bya //
T02TD1360E:164b-0: @164b shes rab ye shes gyis [*kyis] srid pa'i //
T02TD1360E:164b-2: rtsa ba'i ltung bas dmyal bar bsreg / ltung ba dag pas dbang bdun la //
T02TD1360E:164b-3: gnas pa yon tan gyis sbyang bya //
T02TD1360E:164b-4: bum pa gsang gnas brgyal ni //
T02TD1360E:164b-5: brtul zhugs pa yi dbang gis te //
T02TD1360E:164b-6: rtsa ltung byas nas slar yang ni //
T02TD1360E:164b-8: gnang thob tshogs nang 'jug pa na //
T02TD1360E:164b-9: slar yang rgan nas gzhon spang ngo //
T02TD1360E:164b-10: de nas sngags kyi dbang bskur sbyin //
T02TD1360E:164b-11: dbang bdun gyi ni cho ga'o //
T02TD1360E:164b-12: da ni bum pa'i dbang bskur ba //
T02TD1360E:164b-13: bdag ni bde gshegs kun gyi lam //
T02TD1360E:164b-14: dpal ldan bla ma khyed kyi ni //
T02TD1360E:164b-15: bka' drin gyis ni bdag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1360E:164b-16: bla ma khyed dang sangs rgyas dang //
T02TD1360E:164b-17: byang chub sems dpa' ma gtogs par //
T02TD1360E:164b-18: slob dpon gzhan ni mnyes mi bgyi //
T02TD1360E:164b-19: de ltar gsol ba btab nas ni //
T02TD1360E:164b-21: re kh'a lnga yis spras pa yi //
T02TD1360E:164b-23: de ru slob pa ma bzhag nas ni //
T02TD1360E:164b-24: brgyad dang de bzhin bzhin yis ni //
T02TD1360E:164b-25: bum pa nor bu gser gyi 'am //
T02TD1360E:164b-26: sa las byung ba rin chen bcas //
T02TD1360E:164b-27: sman dang dri dang ldan pa yi //
T02TD1360E:164b-28: rgyal dang rnam rgyal bum pa yis //
T02TD1360E:164b-29: shing stegs dbus su bkru bar bya //
T02TD1360E:164b-30: klu yi dpal gyi cod pan bcings //
T02TD1360E:164b-31: nor gyi dpal gyi 'dab ma la //
T02TD1360E:164b-32: bzhi yis bkru dang dar gyis bcings //
T02TD1360E:164b-33: phyag rgya dpal bum gcig gis te //
T02TD1360E:164b-35: ri mo lnga ni rnam par spangs //
T02TD1360E:164b-36: dang po chu la sogs pa yis //
T02TD1360E:164b-37: dge bsnyen du ni 'gyur ba yin //
T02TD1360E:164b-38: bum pa yis ni dge tshul 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:164b-39: gsang dbang dge slong du 'gyur te //
T02TD1360E:164b-40: gnas brtan 'gyur ba gong ma'i rgyu //
T02TD1360E:164b-41: de nas rdor gsum phyag rgya sbyin //
T02TD1360E:164b-42: khyab 'jug thugs su bya ba'i phyir //
T02TD1360E:164b-43: phyag rgya drug lnga cod pan sbyin //
T02TD1360E:164b-44: tshangs pa'i sku phyir mchod phyir thogs //
T02TD1360E:164b-45: dbang phyug gsung du bya ba'i phyir //
T02TD1360E:164b-46: rang gi rgyal po'i rigs dbang gis //
T02TD1360E:164b-47: der ni phyag rgya sbyin bar bya //
T02TD1360E:164b-48: de ltar sku gsung thugs dbang dang //
T02TD1360E:164b-49: lung bstan dang ni dbugs dbyung dang //
T02TD1360E:164b-50: mig thur nyon mongs spang ba dang //
T02TD1360E:164b-51: me long ye shes dbang dang ni //
T02TD1360E:164b-52: chos dang phrin las gnang ba dang //
T02TD1360E:164b-53: slob dpon gyi ni las rnams dang //
T02TD1360E:164b-54: dam tshig rnams ni bsgrag par bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-2: rab tu gnas pa tsam du bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-3: steng du bla re bres nas ni //
T02TD1360E:165a-4: sa yi steng gi gnas dag tu //
T02TD1360E:165a-5: kun nas ming yig gsum bri'o //
T02TD1360E:165a-6: de rnams mtshams su gzhag par bya'o //
T02TD1360E:165a-7: nor bu gser gyi bum pa rnams //
T02TD1360E:165a-8: chu bcas gang pa padma'i khar //
T02TD1360E:165a-9: gser gyi snod dang dngul la sogs //
T02TD1360E:165a-10: yang na dngul las byung ba la //
T02TD1360E:165a-11: dri yi chu ni gzhag par bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-12: nang du gser las byung ba'i stegs //
T02TD1360E:165a-13: nges pa kho nar gzhag par bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-14: de ru khrus ni brtsam par bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-15: me tog la sogs dris bdugs la //
T02TD1360E:165a-16: nyi ma med la bsros pa yis //
T02TD1360E:165a-17: lha rnams la ni byug par bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-18: phye ma rnams kyis mnyes nas ni //
T02TD1360E:165a-19: sbrang rtsi zho dang mar rnams dang //
T02TD1360E:165a-20: 'o ma'i chu yis bkru bar bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-21: grub pa'i don du mar me dang //
T02TD1360E:165a-22: 'bras bu sna tshogs mchog gis bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-23: 'di ru byas pa zin nas ni //
T02TD1360E:165a-24: gnas de nas ni bskyod par bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-25: de ni gnas nas bskyod byas nas //
T02TD1360E:165a-26: sku la na bza' dmar pos ni //
T02TD1360E:165a-27: yang dag par ni dgab par bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-28: dpal gyi dkyil 'khor mtha' ru ni //
T02TD1360E:165a-29: sa mnyam gnas su rgyal ba yi //
T02TD1360E:165a-30: ri mo lnga ni bris nas su //
T02TD1360E:165a-32: rang gi rigs kyi phyogs song ba //
T02TD1360E:165a-33: mtshan ma lnga yis brgyan pa yi //
T02TD1360E:165a-34: de yi dbus su gzhag par bya /
T02TD1360E:165a-35: lha dang lha mo'i sku gzugs kyi //
T02TD1360E:165a-36: zhal ni padma logs su bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-37: mchod rten la sogs glegs bam dang //
T02TD1360E:165a-38: de bzhin du ni bris sku la //
T02TD1360E:165a-39: de la sngags pa kha phyogs bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-40: rgyal ba mchog dang lhan cig tu //
T02TD1360E:165a-41: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje ni //
T02TD1360E:165a-42: stong pa'i rang bzhin du zhes bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-43: phyi nas sngon gsungs rnal 'byor la //
T02TD1360E:165a-44: zla ba nyi ma me skyes la //
T02TD1360E:165a-46: rig ma lha mo rdzogs sangs rgyas //
T02TD1360E:165a-47: a'a li k'a li rigs skyes shing //
T02TD1360E:165a-48: rang rang sa bon las skyes rnams //
T02TD1360E:165a-49: snying ga mgrin pa lte ba dang //
T02TD1360E:165a-50: spyi bo spyi gtsug 'khor lo ru //
T02TD1360E:165a-51: rigs kyi dbang gis bsgom par bya //
T02TD1360E:165a-52: de bzhin du ni bsgom bya ba //
T02TD1360E:165a-53: slar la yang ni lha rnams ni //
T02TD1360E:165a-54: ma lus pa yi rang lus la //
T02TD1360E:165a-55: ye shes sems dpa' bkug nas ni //
T02TD1360E:165a-56: gnyi ga mnyam par bya ba'o //
T02TD1360E:165a-57: khro bo'i rgyal po rang lus la //
T02TD1360E:165a-58: gzhug dang bcing dang mnyes pa dang //
T02TD1360E:165a-59: ro mnyam bya phyir lha rnams bstim //
T02TD1360E:165b-0: de nas slob dpon nyid @165b kyis ni //
T02TD1360E:165b-1: lha rnams zhal bsil phyag ni bya //
T02TD1360E:165b-2: lha dang lha mo rnams kyis ni //
T02TD1360E:165b-3: sa bon aa sogs ka sogs dang //
T02TD1360E:165b-4: rang rig yon tan gyis song ba //
T02TD1360E:165b-5: snying gi dbus su sa bon te //
T02TD1360E:165b-6: zla ba nyi ma sbyangs pa yi //
T02TD1360E:165b-7: sku dang gsung dang thugs su ldan //
T02TD1360E:165b-8: sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan ldan zhing //
T02TD1360E:165b-9: lus ni ma lus par son pa'i //
T02TD1360E:165b-10: mkha' brgyad gsal byed rnams ni 'god //
T02TD1360E:165b-11: de nyid dbyangs kyis phye ba ni //
T02TD1360E:165b-12: glegs bam rnams kyi yi ge dang //
T02TD1360E:165b-13: 'dab ma la ni rnam par dgod //
T02TD1360E:165b-14: mchod rten nang du dpal 'khor lo //
T02TD1360E:165b-15: me dang nor bu padma yi //
T02TD1360E:165b-16: dbus su ral gri'i ri mo'o //
T02TD1360E:165b-17: h'um las gyur pa'i bgrang phreng ni //
T02TD1360E:165b-18: ri lu yongs su bgrang ba ni //
T02TD1360E:165b-19: gsal byed rnams kyi mtshan nyid do //
T02TD1360E:165b-20: dril bu'i lus la dbyangs rnams te //
T02TD1360E:165b-21: bcu yi sum 'gyur byas pa yi //
T02TD1360E:165b-22: ka sogs sde tshan rdo rje ma //
T02TD1360E:165b-23: mchod phyir thogs la sogs pa dang //
T02TD1360E:165b-24: gong ma bcu yis bgrangs pa yi //
T02TD1360E:165b-25: gsal byed rnams ni sgrol byed la //
T02TD1360E:165b-26: ka sogs sde tshan gug skyed bcas //
T02TD1360E:165b-27: nam mkhar ro dang yon tan rnams //
T02TD1360E:165b-28: rnal 'byor rang la bsgom par bya //
T02TD1360E:165b-29: ha h'a dpal gyi rna cha la //
T02TD1360E:165b-30: wa ni zung gcig mgul do dang //
T02TD1360E:165b-31: ske rags dag la dgod pa'o //
T02TD1360E:165b-32: de bzhin yi ge ya ni zung //
T02TD1360E:165b-33: gdu bu dag la dgod par bya //
T02TD1360E:165b-34: g-yer kha rnams la ha h'a gnyis //
T02TD1360E:165b-35: rnam pa lnga yi stong pa ni //
T02TD1360E:165b-36: lus ni ma lus par khyab pa'i //
T02TD1360E:165b-37: thal ba yang ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD1360E:165b-38: rang lus ye shes rnam pa 'o //
T02TD1360E:165b-39: rigs gsum gtso bo lhan cig pa'o //
T02TD1360E:165b-40: phung po khams sogs kun la sogs //
T02TD1360E:165b-41: rang gi snying gi padma ni //
T02TD1360E:165b-42: sa bon so so'i rim pa yis //
T02TD1360E:165b-43: lha rnams dgod par bya ba ni //
T02TD1360E:165b-44: mchod rten lder sol sogs la //
T02TD1360E:165b-45: sa bon bkod pas rab gnas 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:165b-46: rang gi lus las bon dbab //
T02TD1360E:165b-47: lag pa la ni rigs kyi gtso //
T02TD1360E:165b-48: sdud pa yi ni dus su min //
T02TD1360E:165b-49: ri mor bris pa'i bris sku rnams //
T02TD1360E:165b-50: 'di ru me long la ni khrus //
T02TD1360E:165b-51: byas nas dri dang spos dang ni //
T02TD1360E:165b-52: dri zhi ma me tog gis mchod bya //
T02TD1360E:165b-53: glu dang gar dang rol mo dang //
T02TD1360E:165b-54: gos kyi mchog ni sna tshogs pa //
T02TD1360E:165b-55: rnga yab gdugs rnams kyis ni mchod //
T02TD1360E:165b-56: de ltar rab gnas byas nas ni //
T02TD1360E:165b-57: dri yi mchog ni sna tshogs pas //
T02TD1360E:165b-58: dge 'dun la ni ston mo bya //
T02TD1360E:165b-59: khron pa rdzing dang mtshe'u dang //
T02TD1360E:166a-2: klu yi rgyal po rnams ni dgod //
T02TD1360E:166a-3: mtshon bdun rang gi sa bon ni //
T02TD1360E:166a-4: sbrang rtsi chu dang ldan pa yi //
T02TD1360E:166a-5: pa yi lnga ni gzhug par bya //
T02TD1360E:166a-6: sbyin sreg mthar ni rdzing sogs su //
T02TD1360E:166a-7: chu lha dkar mo phyag na ni //
T02TD1360E:166a-8: zhags pa bsnams pa bsgom par bya //
T02TD1360E:166a-9: skyed mos tshal dang dpag bsam shing //
T02TD1360E:166a-10: yang na kun du bskyed pa'i shing //
T02TD1360E:166a-11: shing gcig pa la gtor bar bya //
T02TD1360E:166a-12: de nas rab gnas zin pa dang //
T02TD1360E:166a-13: dam pa yi ni man ngag gis //
T02TD1360E:166a-14: rdzogs pa'i dbang rnams rim bzhin sbyin //
T02TD1360E:166a-16: dpa' bo yi ni ston mo bya //
T02TD1360E:166a-17: srid pa rnam pa gsum song ba'i //
T02TD1360E:166a-18: 'jig rten gsum gyi sems can yang //
T02TD1360E:166a-19: ye shes lcags kyus bkug nas ni //
T02TD1360E:166a-20: snying rjes dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur //
T02TD1360E:166a-21: sangs rgyas bdud rtsi'i rdo rje yis //
T02TD1360E:166a-22: lus ni zla ba lta bur 'gyur //
T02TD1360E:166a-23: rdo rje can gyi lam rnyed nas //
T02TD1360E:166a-24: rang gi gnas su gtang bar bya //
T02TD1360E:166a-25: nyon mongs pa dang bral ba las //
T02TD1360E:166a-26: byang chub spyod pa rjes su gzhol //
T02TD1360E:166a-27: de nas dkyil 'khor mdun du ni //
T02TD1360E:166a-28: slob mas yon gyi tshogs rnams dbul //
T02TD1360E:166a-29: lus kyi nang gi drug cha ni //
T02TD1360E:166a-30: lag pa rkang pa dag dang lus //
T02TD1360E:166a-31: yan lag mchog ni sbyin pa dag / slob dpon la ni rab phul na //
T02TD1360E:166a-33: phyag rgya bzang mos rjes su dbye //
T02TD1360E:166a-34: las kyi dbang po rnams las tshig / dbang po rnams kyi nang nas yid //
T02TD1360E:166a-35: yon dang bcas pa dbul bar bya //
T02TD1360E:166a-36: khams kyi nang nas cha drug pa //
T02TD1360E:166a-37: rkang pa gnyis dang phyugs kyi tshogs //
T02TD1360E:166a-38: de kho na yi cha gzhan ni //
T02TD1360E:166a-39: cod pan dar dang do shal dang// gdu bu yang ni de bzhin te ;
T02TD1360E:166a-40: / rna cha ka bo che la sogs //
T02TD1360E:166a-41: slob dpon la ni rab phul zhing //
T02TD1360E:166a-42: rang gi nus pas yon rnams ni //
T02TD1360E:166a-43: dbul lo mi yi bdag po kye //
T02TD1360E:166a-44: ma lus tshogs kyi rigs la yang //
T02TD1360E:166a-45: bsod nams rgyu ru dbul ba ni //
T02TD1360E:166a-46: gzhan gyi don du smon lam gdab //
T02TD1360E:166a-47: bsod nams 'di yis sems can rnams //
T02TD1360E:166a-48: bcom ldan rnam pa gsum gyis ni //
T02TD1360E:166a-49: bla med byang chub thob par shog / de nas bzod par gsol ba ni //
T02TD1360E:166a-50: rang gi snying ga'i padma ru //
T02TD1360E:166a-51: ye shes sems dpa' gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1360E:166a-52: padma'i bar gyi rdul tshon rnams //
T02TD1360E:166a-53: chu bo gtsang mar bsgyur bar bya //
T02TD1360E:166a-54: dam pa dang po'i rgyud rgyal mthong nas bdag gis ni //
T02TD1360E:166b-0: rim bzhin rjes @166b su sbyar gyis rang bzor byas pa min //
T02TD1360E:166b-1: slob ma dam pas gsol btab dor byas kyi //
T02TD1360E:166b-2: nga rgyal la sogs grags pa'i dbang gis min //
T02TD1360E:166b-3: bdag gis cho ga 'di byas pas //
T02TD1360E:166b-4: blo dang ldan pas rtogs pa dang //
T02TD1360E:166b-5: byed po dge ba spel ba dang //
T02TD1360E:166b-6: bstan bcos rnyed dang ldan par shog / dpal yid du 'ong ba'i phreng ba zhes bya ba /
T02TD1360E:166b-7: dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga / dus kyi zhabs chen po dam pa'i snang ba dang ldan pas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1360E:166b-9: // / pandi ta chen po ba ni shr'i dang /
T02TD1360E:166b-10: lo ts'a ba chings yon tan 'bar gyis bsgyur ba'o /
